                    <span>This is one of those books you can't put down.  It was a moving tearful story with you both loving and hating the main character.
<br />I highly recommend this book especially to high school kids.
<br />It gives us a better understanding into middle eastern life years ago.  I recommended this to my granddaughter and this book is now on her English class's required reading list.  She is a Freshman.
<br />Give this one a try.  You will not be disappointed!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A Great Book! I Couldn't put it down!</div>
                    <div>
